 bounds to hold, obtain linear\nconvergence of VBPG, and derive necessary conditions and sufficient conditions\nfor linear convergence relative to a level set for nonsmooth and nonconvex\noptimization problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 05:26:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 01:25:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-05"}
