 hope that this article, together with the\ncodes, will provide both an overview and the details of the key algorithms, and\nthat it will serve as a basis for the development of new applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 13:19:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 04:06:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-11"}
