eement with the observations. The necessary\ncondition for gap opening and the final planet position depend on the planet\nmass and disc viscosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 13:38:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
