duction of the total cost. Moreover, the decentralized\napproach proposed in this paper demonstrate better scalability with less\naverage computation required.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 04:44:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-28"}
